playing it already for a long time (as I'm one of the WO2097
developers) and I'm still doing. In fact I played my last races a
half an hour ago and did absolutely incredible best race/lap times :)

I'm also glad to say, that the production release works very stable
here, although we all know, that it depends very much on the
heating of the graphics hardware.

The AMIGA version of WO2097 is near at release, the programmers already
