That's similar to polygon reduction, which helps to reduce bus traffic.
It would really help the AMIGA-3D users, as they usually have slow bus,
but there is one problem: a game must be designed to support this
technique in the first place. Trying to add such a feature later is
usually very difficult. I thought about doing something like that
for WO2097, but it simply was much too difficult.

